Insider Activity


Individual




Daniel J. Brestle



Mr. Daniel J. Brestle is Independent Director at DineEquity, Inc. and Chairman-Contributions at Personal Care Products Council Foundation. He is on the Board of Directors at Airborne, Inc., DineEquity, Inc., Cosmetic, Toiletry & Fragrance Association, Bite Tech, Inc., and Shore Memorial Health Foundation.
Mr. Brestle was previously employed as Vice Chairman & President-North America Division by Estee Lauder Cos., Inc., a Principal by Johnson & Johnson, and Senior Advisor by GF Capital Private Equity Management LLC. He also served on the board at Bite Tech, Inc. and Abercrombie & Fitch Co.
He received his undergraduate degree from Villanova University.



