Daniel J. Brestle

Age : 71Public asset : 698,016 USDLinked companies :  DineEquity Inc 





Summary 



Mr. Daniel J. Brestle is on the Board of Directors at DineEquity, Inc., Bite Tech, Inc., Shore Memorial Health Foundation and Cosmetic, Toiletry & Fragrance Association. Mr. Brestle was previously employed as Vice Chairman & President-North America Division by Estee Lauder Cos., Inc., Senior Advisor by GF Capital Private Equity Management LLC, a Principal by Johnson & Johnson, and Chairman-Contributions by Personal Care Products Council Foundation.He also served on the board at Bite Tech, Inc., Airborne, Inc. and Abercrombie & Fitch Co.He received his undergraduate degree from Villanova University.



